vim - vi improved

+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|  Command  		|	Description			|
+-----------------------+---------------------------------------+
| dd			| delete whole line			|
| d3 			| delete next 3 line			|
+-----------------------+---------------------------------------+
| u 			| to undo				| 
| r 			| to redo				|
+-----------------------+---------------------------------------+
| / and n  		| searching and next result		|
+-----------------------+---------------------------------------+
| set number 		| to see line number			|
| set relativenumber 	| to see relative number		|
| set nonumber  	| remove damn numbers			|
+-----------------------+---------------------------------------+
| shift + a or $ 	| to go to end of line			|
| 0 			| to go to start of line		|
+-----------------------+---------------------------------------+
| 12G			| jumps to line number 12		|
+-----------------------+---------------------------------------+
| :%s/old/new		| s for string / replace old word with	|
|			| new Exp -  :%s/nginx/jalebi		|
+-----------------------+---------------------------------------+
